Thanks for all the nice comments! I noticed yesterday morning that Dougie's back left leg was buckling and just giving out on him. The vet diagnosed him with luxating patella, which is a fancy way of saying his kneecaps pop out. She recommended limiting his activity for a few days and maybe seeing a specialist since he's only 3 and it might get worse. He's not in any pain though, and he was thrilled to be at the vet getting scratchies from everyone. Still 18 pounds though.
